<div class="userstuff">
  <h3 class="heading" id="introduction">introduction</h3>
  <p>hi i'm <a href="https://eunoia.sayitditto.net/">melo</a>. i'm a random loser who decided to self host otw-archive on a macbook (it runs linux btw) because i thought it'd be funny. i do this for fun so be nice to me. you can do whatever but please read and follow my <%= link_to ts("rules"), tos_path %>.<br><br>
  
  this is invite only and i approve and deny invite requests based on if i know you or if the vibes are good or bad. good luck<br><br>
  
  also i named this after a tinashe song. it bangs. listen to it<br><br>
  
